Q. How to pass parameter to an apex method and Apex method with return type.
here we will pass parameter from annonamous window.

public class AnnoPara {
    public static void param(string name){
        system.debug('hi how are you' + name);
    }   
    public static void param2(Integer age){
        system.debug('your are is ' + age + 'year old girl !!!!');
    }
}



public class AnnoPara {
    public static void param(string name){
        system.debug('hi how are you' + name);
    }
    public static void division(Integer a , Integer b){
        Integer c = a/b ; 
        system.debug('the divisio of a & b is' + c);
    }
 }



Now we are talking about return type


public class AnnoPara {
    public static String name(){ // if we are mention here string.
        system.debug('khusbu');
        return 'khusbu';  // then we need to pass string in return.
    }
 }
